void '''SetShade''' (color ''col'')

==Usage==
Sets the {{Property|StencilColor|stencil color}} of the actor.

===Parameters===
*''col'': The color to set. This can either be a name, like {{c|"Red"}} or a hexadecimal value, like {{c|"FF0000"}}.

==Examples==
This {{Class|cacodemon}} turns completely red upon death.
 class Caco : Cacodemon
 {
     States
     {
     Death:
         HEAD A 0
         {
             [[A_SetRenderStyle]](1.0, {{const|STYLE_Stencil}});
             '''SetShade'''("FF0000");
         }
         Goto Super::Death;
     }
 }

